        {
            "title": "英偉達執行長黃仁勳據悉計畫前往中國",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"英偉達執行長黃仁勳據悉計畫前往中國\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/hJD.x8xiQlxO6MpU8uR1ug--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-01/cc227bc0-ea84-11f0-bfa9-9c10607c253a\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">英偉達執行長黃仁勳據悉計畫前往中國</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
